{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "5c512ab9-2cbb-4a89-9ec6-df7275c81591", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/5c512ab9-2cbb-4a89-9ec6-df7275c81591@1.pkg/1772597680975/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597681965", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/5c512ab9-2cbb-4a89-9ec6-df7275c81591@1.pkg/1772597680975/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597681965"}, "identifier": "5c512ab9-2cbb-4a89-9ec6-df7275c81591", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>本题考查 &ldquo;正确看待顺境和逆境&rdquo; 的知识点。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>鲁迅在面对国家困境和创作阻力时，没有放弃理想，而是以坚定信念积极行动（以笔为刃唤醒国人），体现了面对逆境的正确态度。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">②</span><span>：&ldquo;坚守信念、迎难而上&rdquo; 符合鲁迅在挫折中不退缩的做法，正确；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">④</span><span>：&ldquo;保持斗志、积极作为&rdquo; 体现了他以实际行动应对逆境的态度，正确；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①</span><span>：&ldquo;退缩逃避、放弃理想&rdquo; 是消极对待逆境的表现，与鲁迅的选择不符；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">③</span><span>：&ldquo;消极抱怨、随波逐流&rdquo; 是面对挫折的懈怠行为，不符合题意；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>答案选 C。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">（改编）</span><span>鲁迅在青年时期目睹国家积弱、民众愚昧，曾因 &ldquo;医治精神比医治身体更重要&rdquo; 而弃医从文。他在创作道路上屡遭质疑和压迫，作品多次被查禁，但始终以笔为刃，用文字唤醒国人意识，留下《呐喊》《彷徨》等经典著作。鲁迅的经历告诉我们，面对逆境和挫折应（ ）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①</span><span>退缩逃避、放弃理想</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">②</span><span>坚守信念、迎难而上</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">③</span><span>消极抱怨、随波逐流</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">④</span><span>保持斗志、积极作为</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）鲁迅在青年时期目睹国家积弱、民众愚昧，曾因 “医治精神比医治身体更重要” 而弃医从文。他在创作道路上屡遭质疑和压迫，作品多次被查禁，但始终以笔为刃，用文字唤醒国人意识，留下《呐喊》《彷徨》等经典著作。鲁迅的经历告诉我们，面对逆境和挫折应（ ）①退缩逃避、放弃理想②坚守信念、迎难而上③消极抱怨、随波逐流④保持斗志、积极作为", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/5c512ab9-2cbb-4a89-9ec6-df7275c81591@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754984697872", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①②</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "